				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: When is it possible in PoN?<a name="46982"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 18 04 7:39 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>    PoN is easily managable at lvl52 best to have an earing of the solstice.  If your short on money go swarm kite Dulak harbor incredibly easy and good exp all the way to 55 so you really shouldn't even be here.  However charm kiting here theres a 1/5 resist ratio wich means one of every five charms is resisted.  The nightstalkers are more resistent to cold than anything else.  Be carefull not to overpull them because they can kill a charmed nightstalker in under 3 seconds.  Tend to pull them 5 at a time so you have time to invis and still maintain good dps.  Minimal adds in the area.  You get some form of diamond every 2 kills.  A semi-rare Decaying Bone idol Summong 5 for a necro.  A runed chain cap i believe is the only rare, and Peridots drop consistently.
<br />

<br />
-Jareen Xegony Bard</span></td>
