			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: When is it possible in PoN?<a name="54707"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 2 04 1:17 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Whenever nightstalkers are taken by this one bard that sucks I go to Natimbi and Swarm the restless souls. This is difficult because you can only charm the males AND some males are too high to be charmed (level 52). This is a great camp for honing your bardliness. If you end up with a kite that has no more potential pets then there are some stairs up the hill with 2 roaming mastruq. Charm a mastruq and send it in. These pets are very good damage because they proc a huge DD very often. This should beat down a pet considerably. I have found that outright a mastruq will kill a soul, but 2 souls will kill a mastruq and leave the one soul at like 30-40%. If those don't finish them off grab a wandering animal or just chant them down. There has been a change to Natimbi where the named mobs now summon. This is no good for us as if Tumia Lehio pops in your souls camp she will need to be dispatched to continue exp.
<br />

<br />
tips for this camp:
<br />
1) Have more than FT 1. There are a lot of resists here.
<br />
2) Have a high level alt, or a friend that will kill tumia for you.
<br />
3) Make a hotkey &quot;/say %s&quot; this will identify the gender of your target.
<br />
4)Learn to love target toggling
<br />

<br />
What is target toggling?
<br />

<br />
Go in to your keyboard section of the options window and select the targeting tab. There is a button that you can set for toggling the last two targets you had. I set this to the num pad /. Target your pet and your pets target and use this to switch. Theres also a cycle nearest npc's key. I set this to `. Tap it and it will cycle through the NPC's in your swarm in order, you can use this to 1) find a girl to make your pet kill and 2) find a boy to charm.
<br />

<br />
I hope this helps. Its a nice way to spend your time when you can't play in PoN.
<br />

<br />
FUN TIP! Restless souls drop Spectral Essence. Collect four and talk to a man by the Magus on thebeach, he will have a mace for you.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%"><center><a href="http://www.roi-guild.com"><img src="http://img78.photobucket.com/albums/v291/Stormwave/Lorta.jpg" alt="Lorta Sig" border="0" /></a></center></span></td>
