				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: When is it possible in PoN?<a name="54882"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 3 04 7:05 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Yeah, after two levels (56 &amp; 57) and 6AA's Ravenous Nightstalkers got old, plus all the a-holes druids pulling from my camp, I spent probably 20 hours there this weekend!!  Got to love tribute!!  When I would got to log the first night, I had 15 Blue Diamonds, 20 Raw Diamonds and 13 Diamonds, plus tons of claws, letters and runes.  I would take 10 diamonds, at 200 Favor points each is 2000 Favor points, which is more then enough for 10 hours of FT4, actually lowered it to FT3 the second day, FT4 was to much.  But, 15k , two levels and 6 AA's is not bad for 20 hours work.  
<br />

<br />
Saturday night, I decided to explore a bit and headed to Natimbi.  Great zone, crowded but still Restless Souls were a great change of pace.  First, the Mastruq summon, not just the named, but the regular Mastruq walking up and down the steps, so be quick on your notes if you are charming them.  At 57 the Restless Souls were giving about double the exp Ravenous Nightstalkers were, but the AA xp seemed better at Nightstalkers?  2% constant AA xp for the Restless and 2-3% for the Nightstalkers.  
<br />

<br />
Now that I have RS3, I will probably give Nadox a few circles.
<br />

<br />
Oh yeah, I had two Spectral essences drop in the hour I was swarming the Restless!!  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-4.gif" border="0" alt="Tongue out" hspace="2" /></span></td>
